Klasse GameDataBridge

java.lang.Object
viewmodel.GameDataBridge
public class GameDataBridge extends Object
Manages game state data and provides a bridge between the client and the UI. This class handles player data, robot models, game phases, and various game mechanics such as checkpoints, energy, upgrades, and damage.
